Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average resolution time of 'Accepted + Assigned'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Assigned and the end of the case

Name: Total time for 'Accepted + Assigned' to transition to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum time from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average time it takes 'Accepted + Assigned' after the execution of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Total time it takes 'Accepted + Assigned' to be done before 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Accepted + Assigned' in cases leading to 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Minimum time it takes 'Accepted + Assigned' after 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' is performed
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Completed + Resolved' in the most frequent variant
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total resolution time of 'Accepted + Assigned' in variants leading to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average time for 'Accepted + Assigned' before 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' in the process flow
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Minimum time for 'Accepted + Assigned' to transition to any 'Completed' status activity
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed'

Name: Average time it takes 'Accepted + Assigned' to be done after 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Total time from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Accepted + In Progress' in cases with high impact
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'begin': "activity == 'Accepted + Assigned'", 'end': "activity == 'Accepted + In Progress'", 'aggregation': 'total', 'filter': 'impact > high'}

Name: Average time for 'Accepted + Assigned' in cases ending with 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'
